To create her video work "Cosmic Generator," Mika Rottenberg filmed in two locations at opposite ends of the earth: a Chinese restaurant in Mexicali and a wholesale market in Yiwu, China. Rottenberg collapses notions of distance and time to consider how masses of plastic objects sold in Yiwu Market circulate the globe freely and rapidly, while people and certain products face greater restrictions to crossing the US-Mexico border. See "Cosmic Generator" as part of "Mika Rottenberg: Easypieces," now on view. #MikaRottenberg
